e supernova mechanism per se, our simulations support\nthe theoretical conclusion (already reached by others) that spherical (1D)\nsupernovae do not explode when good physics and transport methods are employed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 10 Nov 2002 22:15:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 2 Apr 2003 18:22:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-07"}
