present models all the transitions known for the mean-field version of the\nmodel are completely wiped out. Finally we also determine the time\nauto-correlation functions of individual spins, and show that the system is\ndynamically very heterogeneous.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 11 Nov 2002 07:07:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-07"}
