ed. Finally, we discuss how the `trap model' can\nbe adapted to granular materials, such that more subtle `memory' effects can be\naccounted for.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 11 Nov 2002 09:57:12 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 24 Dec 2002 10:40:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-05-23"}
